::Feline::

She looked at HotRod and stood there with her jaw gaping.  She closed 
her mouth and tried to swallow, but couldn't. She couldn't beleive 
what he just told her.  She then remembered thee chip she put in him. 
She then thought how proud Zardus would be of her.

She looked at HotRod. "So that means your.....uh...your.."


KitKat::
is asleep in the chair next to the CR unit.
